body_html:
My stripped retrained model works by following @andrewharp 's suggestion and modifying some source code.

If you got the error messages with your retrained model below:

F/native  (10551): tensorflow_jni.cc:304 Error during inference: Not found: FeedInputs: unable to find feed output input:0
F/libc    (10551): Fatal signal 6 (SIGABRT), code -6 in tid 10570 (InferenceThread)

You also need to modify the class TensorflowImageListener in TensorflowImageListener.java by following the suggestion in its comment (change the values of IMAGE_SIZE, IMAGE_MEAN, IMAGE_STD, INPUT_NAME, and OUTPUT_NAME).

body:
My stripped retrained model works by following @andrewharp 's suggestion and modifying some source code.

If you got the error messages with your retrained model below:

```
F/native  (10551): tensorflow_jni.cc:304 Error during inference: Not found: FeedInputs: unable to find feed output input:0
F/libc    (10551): Fatal signal 6 (SIGABRT), code -6 in tid 10570 (InferenceThread)
```

You also need to modify the class `TensorflowImageListener` in `TensorflowImageListener.java` by following the suggestion in its comment (change the values of `IMAGE_SIZE`, `IMAGE_MEAN`, `IMAGE_STD`, `INPUT_NAME`, and `OUTPUT_NAME`).
